-- GLG Hires Tisbury's Griffin, Lucaussy to Oversee Event-Driven Strategies
-- Tom Cahill
-- 2010-04-20T08:07:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-04-20/glg-hires-tisbury-s-griffin-lucaussy-to-oversee-event-driven-strategies.html

          
          
             GLG Partners Inc. said Gerard
Griffin and Gerald Lucaussy of Tisbury Capital Management will
join the hedge fund furm to oversee its event-driven strategies.
GLG commented in an e-mailed statement today.  
